About this hotel

Off a rural road, this regal hotel on lush grounds is 10 km from the 19th-century Bahia Palace and 16 km from Marrakesh Menara Airport.

    Price doesn’t warrant service
    The resort is beautiful but unable to accommodate a full booking for an event.

    I have to start my review by thanking the staff of Palais Ronsard for what was an unforgettable stay. From the moment I was greeted at the door I felt welcome. The place is absolutely beautiful with no attention to detail spared. The rooms were oversized, the ceilings high, and they are decorated beautifully.     Annakhil

    The sprawling suburb of Annakhil includes golf courses and palm groves, with paths and horse-carriage tours through 100,000 trees at El Palmeral. Inside that park is Musée de la Palmeraie, showing a century of Moroccan paintings in a 1940s colonial farmhouse. MACAAL is a more modern space, displaying pan-African art. Residential areas have casual tagine restaurants, while resort hotels have chic bars and bistros.

    About this hotel

    Off a rural road, this regal hotel on lush grounds is 10 km from the 19th-century Bahia Palace and 16 km from Marrakesh Menara Airport. …

    Featuring coffered ceilings and marble bathrooms, the airy, plush suites offer terraces, fireplaces and sitting areas. Villas add private plunge pools. All provide satellite TV, free Wi-Fi, minibars and Nespresso machines. Some have claw-foot tubs.

    Amenities include an outdoor pool, 2 restaurants, 2 bars and a garden. There’s also a spa with a sauna, a hammam and a fitness center. Breakfast and an airport shuttle are available (fee). Children age 12 and over are welcome.
